### /api/v1/trigger [POST]
#### Puts the query results to the database and triggers redis channels.

+ Parameteres
    + query object (string) - An object with key as query, and a value as a string. (e.g: language:javascript)
+ to send the trigger use curl
    + curl -X POST -d query='string' url_address/api/v1/trigger

+ Request (application/x-www-form-urlencoded)
        
    + Headers

            Location: /api/v1/trigger

    + Body

            {
                "query": "RisingStack-bootcamp"
            }

+ Response 201

    + Body

+ Response 400

    + Body 
    
            { 
                errors: { 
                    query: [ 
                        '"query" is not allowed to be empty' 
                    ] 
                } 
            }
        
+ Response 400
        
    + Body 
    
            {
                errors: {
                    query: [
                        '"query"' is required'
                    ]
                }
            }
            
